title: [Feymist Cemetery, Briar Thicket]
description: An impenetrable briar thicket surrounds you to the west, north, and east, blocking further exploration of this foul smelling mire.  A lone crypt, nearly lost in the mass of briars, is the only structure still standing amidst piles of broken headstones.

An impenetrable briar thicket surrounds you to the east and west, blocking further exploration of this foul smelling mire.  To the north, the underbrush has been cut back and a narrow pathway can be traversed.  A lone crypt, nearly lost in the mass of briars, is the only structure still standing amidst piles of broken headstones.
